import warnings

warnings.filterwarnings("ignore")

r"""
================================================================================
U(4) TOPOLOGICAL GRAND UNIFICATION 
Script 4: The Unified Flavor & CKM Engine (Full Matrix RGE)
================================================================================
This script unifies the flavor sector by evaluating the full 3x3 Yukawa matrices. 

It proves that the CKM mixing angles are not arbitrary parameters, but emerge 
